    <title>Introduction to lazarus</title>

    <para><!-- copied from https://www.lazarus-ide.org/ -->
      Lazarus is a Delphi compatible cross-platform IDE for Rapid
      Application Development. It has variety of components ready
      for use and a graphical form designer to easily create complex
      graphical user interfaces.
    </para>

